generalComment.value:
Site-specific data refer to the year 2021. Proxy data were used for less than 0,32% of the mass balance.


By mass (production)


The cut-off rules have been used during data collection through hypothesis and simplification. Some auxiliary materials used within the production process have been excluded from the study. These simplifications respect
the rules defined by the PCR standard used.
